@node HISTORY "Update History"
37.6 Additions:
   @{"ASSIGNSYS" link ASSIGNSYS} Option
   @{"Workbench" link WB} now saves options as tool types.
   New format for @{"AmigaDOS" link DOS} display of current features.

37.5 Additions:
   AmigaDOS @{"WINDOW" link WINDOW} Option
   Changed @{"AmigaDOS" link DOS} template to keyword format
   Workbench now parses tooltypes; user can configure program without DOS
   Does not open window upon first installation; usable with WBStartup
   @{"BORDERBLANK" link BORDERBLANK} now affects all open screens

37.4 Additions:
   @{"CENTERWINDOW" link CENTERWINDOW} Option
   @{"REQTOOLS" link REQTOOLS} Option

   Replaced portion of program that depended on v39 utility.library.
   No longer has illegal instruction errors under Workbench 2.1 and below.

37.3 Additions:
   @{"Workbench" link WB} interface
   @{"DISKMUTE" link DISKMUTE} Option

37.2 Additions:
   @{"WILDSTAR" link WILDSTAR} Option

37.1 Creation:
   Integration of CreateDirPatch, NewLook, DashReq into one DOS command.

I apologize for any inconvenience that may occur due to undetected
programming errors.  I am only able to test this program with a 68030
and Workbench 3.0, but this program is intended to be compatible with
V2.0/2.1 machines and 68000 and 68040 processors as well.  Please @{"report" link IE}
any incompatibilities with your system to me immediately.  Thank you.
@endnode

